        <p data-role="text">Mr An&#xAD;thony Chai and Ms Jade Ng at their stu&#xAD;dio space in Jurong East. They forked out about $40,000 to ren&#xAD;o&#xAD;vate the rented space. They kept costs low through do-it-your&#xAD;self projects, and paint&#xAD;ing the walls and in&#xAD;stalling lights by them&#xAD;selves.</p>
    </div>

